{"tid":1120103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"當年讀U無嘢做, 開發左個有得炒股票牛熊證期權既大富翁","createTime":"2019-04-22T11:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T02:22:10.000Z","uid":235547,"like":57,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dff276cce87b165bb901667558e81429a39533ea","tid":1120103,"uid":235547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:56:15.000Z","msg":"今日假期, 無聊睇下當年做過啲乜, 無意中發現左一個已經發晒毛, 無再玩好耐既Tailor made大富翁。<br />\n<br />\n先介紹下啲角色:<br />\n一般玩家(MAX 8人): 佢地會用LEGO人仔當係Token 咁用, 玩法同一般大富翁基本一樣, 買地收租, 但就多左幾個OPTION賺錢, 炒股, 炒樓, 炒牛熊, 炒期權, 炒埋VIX期貨都有, 下面再講。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d25289_1fa5f5efc3de48e48a19ebe99b3450bd.jpg/v1/fill/w_358,h_268,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01/d25289_1fa5f5efc3de48e48a19ebe99b3450bd.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd25289_1fa5f5efc3de48e48a19ebe99b3450bd.jpg%2Fv1%2Ffill%2Fw_358%2Ch_268%2Cal_c%2Cq_80%2Cusm_0.66_1.00_0.01%2Fd25289_1fa5f5efc3de48e48a19ebe99b3450bd.webp&h=5bc90769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一個角色叫做Banker, 佢就同玩家一齊行, 佢負責賣車及其他High Class嘢加炒股, 佢會諗辦法喺玩家身上搶錢, 例如扼佢地買牛熊期權等等, 整肥自己。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d25289_4c72a7ddd649473ca9fd41e4ddb9e280.png/v1/fill/w_354,h_265,al_c,lg_1,q_80/d25289_4c72a7ddd649473ca9fd41e4ddb9e280.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd25289_4c72a7ddd649473ca9fd41e4ddb9e280.png%2Fv1%2Ffill%2Fw_354%2Ch_265%2Cal_c%2Clg_1%2Cq_80%2Fd25289_4c72a7ddd649473ca9fd41e4ddb9e280.webp&h=eb2facfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後一個角色係政府, 佢負責賣地同出糧比玩家, 減少貧富懸殊問題, 另外佢為左收支平衡, 都要炒股票投資。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d25289_0c52dc95748c43adbb500611183f8e11.jpg/v1/fill/w_358,h_268,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01/d25289_0c52dc95748c43adbb500611183f8e11.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd25289_0c52dc95748c43adbb500611183f8e11.jpg%2Fv1%2Ffill%2Fw_358%2Ch_268%2Cal_c%2Cq_80%2Cusm_0.66_1.00_0.01%2Fd25289_0c52dc95748c43adbb500611183f8e11.webp&h=aa3179f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3個角色加埋可以有10人玩緊, 果時人緣都OK, 好易搵到咁多人一齊玩, 諗番都正。<br />\n<br />\n投資項目: 炒樓<br />\n整個地圖又6張A4紙組成, 所以有好多地可以玩, 如果儲得愈多同色地區, 租金會增加。<br />\n另外, 租金會按股市表現有掛鈎, 個市升得勁, 啲樓價同租都會上, 而且公益福利卡有啲會影響到樓市個加乘, 試過啲租搞到比原價貴42倍。<br />\n地鐵站收租則睇下有多人踩過, 愈多人踩, 車費(租)愈貴, 去到尾, 會貴到顛。<br />\n<br />\n另外除左玩家買地之外, 去到車行可以同銀行買車, 有錢之後, 可以行快啲甚至避開交租。但買左車之後要交稅比政府, 基本上每行一圈, 就少一筆錢, 啲人工唔夠比車稅, 所以買左車就係為左快啲炒樓炒股。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d25289_31bd71b5800e4e3293fa61c99fd2c863.jpg/v1/fill/w_358,h_258,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01/d25289_31bd71b5800e4e3293fa61c99fd2c863.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd25289_31bd71b5800e4e3293fa61c99fd2c863.jpg%2Fv1%2Ffill%2Fw_358%2Ch_258%2Cal_c%2Cq_80%2Cusm_0.66_1.00_0.01%2Fd25289_31bd71b5800e4e3293fa61c99fd2c863.webp&h=7d262f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於啲金額都唔細, 所以玩親都碌卡或者搵銀行過數。<br />\n<br />\n去到股票市場, 呢個可謂搞左最耐既位, 應該前前後後SET左3年。<br />\n成個System用Excel + VBA咁整, 可隨時轉換中英VERSION。<br />\n玩家經過銀行時就可以買賣任何投資產品, 股票牛熊證期權, 甚至引伸波幅期貨都有, 另外玩家可以選擇比電腦幫佢地操盤, 係....玩到有ALGO喺里面同真人玩家鬥。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YWO2XCy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYWO2XCy.png&h=19b510ab&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n咁升跌點定呢?<br />\n就係銀行同政府行走時,  同一般玩家一樣, 其中2粒骰決定佢地行走幾多格, 但佢地要擲多一粒骰, 第三粒骰就會決定升定跌, 而之前果2粒骰就會決定升跌多少$, 例如第三粒骰決定左係跌, 如果另外2粒擲左加埋12,咁個市就會無$12, 所以衰運上嚟, 可以一路跌。<br />\n另外, 如果玩家買一手(一手價錢 = 股價X100 同港交所一樣), 就會升幫手推升$0.1。如果買350手(最大每次買賣量), 就可以推高$35。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外, 玩家可以玩埋牛熊證, IV期貨, 期權, 規則就同現實世界差唔多, 每15ROUND結算一次。由於夾爆牛熊證會按照對沖值再額外推個市一獲, 另外期權可以同唔同對家SHORT LONG, 所以通常銀行,政府同大戶 三邊角力, 諗盡辦法夾爆對面, 為左快啲到銀行TRADE, 所以一定買架最貴最快既車玩。每次玩完都講緊幾十億元成交, 唔寫EXCEL玩, 人手計死左好耐。<br />\n<br />\n當年我為左個GAME都整左2段片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tTrTfV4v3uI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtTrTfV4v3uI&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0iL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=ca11c543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tTrTfV4v3uI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yGmiwD3mqJo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyGmiwD3mqJo&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0iL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=af729616\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yGmiwD3mqJo</a><br />\n<br />\nAnyway, 果時讀U已經自己玩緊股票, 好著迷金融市場, 所以整埋咁既嘢一嘗大戶感覺, 其實話雖無聊, 但對之後今日都有啲啲幫助, 例如今時今日我就主要做Program Trade, 唔炒牛熊但會做期權等等。<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999, 但希望大家睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0857b357183fc0e71828375178f87858257224ca","tid":1120103,"uid":241596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:59:55.000Z","msg":"好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fbb21ec96b81ce0ca200440835abc031c25d703","tid":1120103,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T12:16:05.000Z","msg":"algo都有咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db456fc6def126da8554567612ade71139a4c93","tid":1120103,"uid":66500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T12:20:20.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8bc2be1a3ac7838e32e3866a03bebb98b019c5a","tid":1120103,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T12:29:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3228ab64f3a3f10cd726ab7419460dce6a1cd908","tid":1120103,"uid":48345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T12:31:25.000Z","msg":"睇落幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db4dff251b8be55e36e5865ccb5ad748f22771d","tid":1120103,"uid":42429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T12:34:56.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"5958875c306e79adebc397c33229345718459340","tid":1120103,"uid":235547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"其實想賣左佢，但咁難玩，都唔知邊個會玩"},{"pid":"bbfbb16753a4586d3598adba3f73d1ce13b0633f","tid":1120103,"uid":241596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:17:07.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e82a35741b2249d689f8c5d57239ba868c49ad","tid":1120103,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5958875c306e79adebc397c33229345718459340","tid":1120103,"uid":235547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"其實想賣左佢，但咁難玩，都唔知邊個會玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:27:14.000Z","msg":"真係幾有趣 幾想玩"},{"pid":"1a91f32800fe256800ecfb79acf26cc00626d5d1","tid":1120103,"uid":235547,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:36:34.000Z","msg":"我得閒就UPLOAD啲嘢上嚟。<br />\n<br />\n最大果4幅因為用AutoCad整, 所以SHOW唔到, 但額外2張用Photoshop之類既嘢整, 所以可以UPLOAD比大家睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xXU56a1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxXU56a1.png&h=38eb0b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yuqw1Kn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYuqw1Kn.png&h=70c40b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最初頭我地用紙幣玩, 但因為我地會SAVE低啲錢作為下次再鬥過, 結果inflation問題, 就愈玩愈大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果時搵左幾個FRIEND幫手PRINT錢, 大學PRINT嘢QUOTA好多時用唔晒,就夜晚喺U到PRINT錢。<br />\n<br />\n結果有個FRIEND夜晚PRINT PRINT下, 比其他人睇到, 果條友呆左, 2條友你眼望我望...唔講以為我個FRIEND痴左線, 喺學校到PRINT死人錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J8iR1KT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ