gine仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659a4ee3ce3395f3bed13128887ee11db80f9a61","tid":1120103,"uid":60150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eb0b6a19cdb2eb6b673afaaa3a05c78ae6a246e","tid":1120103,"uid":235547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab6458c4664e07f133f0474fa64d1676d7d5ed43","tid":1120103,"uid":242834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:43:14.000Z","msg":"CLS 巴打讀邊科"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:43:50.000Z","msg":"Believe it or not, 我係Engine仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:46:21.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇興趣量產變board game<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賺到笑"},{"pid":"e838954576e8de85ce54dda61b407daf8e3af05c","tid":1120103,"uid":235547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9590b5ecc456e01f4d7289a0b2e23ec856baf93","tid":1120103,"uid":2235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:13:46.000Z","msg":"program trade 人工是咪肥肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:50:52.000Z","msg":"我正職唔係Program Trade,自己有其他生意搞,Program Trade只係嗜好, 當玩真人大富翁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5b8f6141b4cdf3d56796deb4502c5af3daf1f6","tid":1120103,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:59:04.000Z","msg":"同monopoly 間廠傾下賣番比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba2faaa16f48830cfc1f82a9f7e9ee4246ffe87","tid":1120103,"uid":235547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:10:12.000Z","msg":"好難SELL得出去<br />\n未計十幾頁紙既RULE, 一般人睇完已經唔想玩。如果玩果班人無一個識金融產品, 仲要解釋埋點炒期權, 牛熊, 起碼講解幾粒鐘, 上完堂未擲骰都番得屋企訓覺。<br />\n另外仲有啲版權問題有排搞, 隻GAME用左 LV, LAMBORGHINI, GUCCI, PORSCHE....品牌, 都唔知點傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3024aa